PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1996-200 of February 20, 1996, which appointed LÉONARD J. LeBLANC as full-time member of the National Parole Board, Atlantic Regional Division by revoking the words "for a period of five years" and substituting the words "for a period ending March 17, 2002; and designation of LÉONARD J. LeBLANC, of Fredericton, New Brunswick, as Vice-Chairperson for the Atlantic region of the National Parole Board to hold office during pleasure, effective March 18, 1997.
